::Aerotaur::
       He stood very still unsure of how Birdbot would react.  He slowly 
circled toward the wall so as to get a clean shot at Birdbot.  Without 
lifting his left hand too high he fired a shot at Birdbot.  He simultaneously 
swung with his bladed staff in his right hand.
